name: Neon #000
description:
This is the primordial photon in #Neon light that gives off a bright luminescence. As the source of all Neon lights, it can generate an unlimited supply and will never go out. They are #cold cathode discharge lamps. Applying a high potential difference of several thousand volts across the electrodes ionizes the gas in the tube and fluoresces colored light.
Owning an edition of this token makes you a #NeónBuddy.
#Neon #000 Primordial Source of Unlimited Energy Acquire one and follow the path of #Light.
